{"tid":1036194,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Steamspy 估計，擁有《還願》的玩家已經突破一百萬人","createTime":"2019-02-25T05:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T06:54:45.000Z","uid":44930,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65437b2625fcc4c2681f8eaf187faf0b89807a83","tid":1036194,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:08:44.000Z","msg":"赤燭遊戲研發的心靈恐怖遊戲《還願》在發生埋梗小熊維尼事件後，在 Steam 暢銷商品排行中，前三名分別是《還願》、《還願》豪華版組合包與《還願》原聲帶，而第四名則是同樣由赤燭製作的《返校》。<br />\n<br />\n根據 Steamspy 統計，擁有本作品的玩家已經超過 100 萬，而《還願》過去三天最多同時遊玩人數超過 13900 人，玩家平均遊玩時間約為 2.2 小時。<br />\n<br />\n《還願》此次埋梗引發眾多中國玩家湧入 Steam 刷負評事件，也引發不少國外媒體關注，包括 Eurogamer、PC Gamer、PCGamesN、Polygon、<a href=\"http://Comicbook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FComicbook.com&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8c4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=226b5a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Comicbook.com</a> 都紛紛報導此次事件。"},{"pid":"aa116fe7dbe80a05588b7dbfcde5cf8b3e7d9597","tid":1036194,"uid":44930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://steamspy.com/app/1006510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamspy.com%2Fapp%2F1006510&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8c4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=7cf67c9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamspy.com/app/1006510</a> <br />\nOwners: 1,000,000 .. 2,000,000"},{"pid":"0f72f98dd0ecc0eac12819e7aa5be09d4f599bdd","tid":1036194,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402cc0397feb3c0c6a941d7993b233214e717ac5","tid":1036194,"uid":29996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:48:19.000Z","msg":"weekend就買黎嚇餐死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06b8270b5837fbcd91130202dfcabb6f250e43b","tid":1036194,"uid":146243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":